OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm end
OL,6,Fto the day with some late evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry overnight with
OL,8,Fclear skies at first. Some cloud
OL,9,Fdeveloping across Cornwall later with
OL,10,Fsome mist and fog patches possible.
OL,11,FTemperatures dipping lower than
OL,12,Frecently.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FAny morning mist and fog
OL,15,Fclearing, with patchy cloud likely to
OL,16,Flinger across Cornwall. Dry and bright
OL,17,Felsewhere with plenty of sunshine.Low
OL,18,Frisk of the odd shower later. Feeling
OL,19,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
